# IntelliJ HTTP Client examples for technical-interview-demo
# Category creation requires ADMIN and an authenticated session.
# Auth errors use the localized ProblemDetail shape with title/status/detail/messageKey/message/language.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@sessionCookie = paste-technical-interview-demo-session-here
@writeCategoryId = 0
### CategoryController - list categories
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Accept: application/json

### CategoryController - create category (ADMIN + authenticated session)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Architecture"
}
> {%
if (response.status === 201) {
  client.global.set("writeCategoryId", String(response.body.id));
}
%}

### CategoryController - create category without authentication (401 localized ProblemDetail)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/problem+json

{
  "name": "Architecture"
}

### CategoryController - create category as non-admin user (403 localized ProblemDetail)
# Replace the session cookie with a regular authenticated USER session.
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/categories
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/problem+json

{
  "name": "Architecture"
}

### CategoryController - update category (ADMIN + authenticated session)
# Run the create request first or replace the id with an existing category.
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/{{writeCategoryId}}
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "name": "Software Architecture"
}

### CategoryController - delete unused category (ADMIN + authenticated session)
# Run the create request first.
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/{{writeCategoryId}}
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}

### CategoryController - delete category assigned to books (409 localized ProblemDetail)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/categories/1
Cookie: technical-interview-demo-session={{sessionCookie}}
Accept: application/problem+json
